<plot>Two hit men are sent to kill the same woman not knowing that they are competing to assassinate her. Showing up at a warehouse in the outskirts of the city, they find the victim with her hands and feet bound. The scene is the starting point of a series of conversations on whom and how to dispose of this woman, the requirements to take a human life being experience, ethics and creativity. The conversations on the study of human anatomy, terrorism, art, and theoretical and self formation will take center stage in this story and lead to a climactic struggle to the death, as the characters forget about the victim and their profession.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?121901</url></doc>
